{"type": "article", "id": 10156, "title": "这个设计了不起之儿童节可以准备起来了", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-05-29T08:05:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 10830, "name": "儿童袜子"}, {"id": 10831, "name": "Miffy"}, {"id": 2284, "name": "桌子"}, {"id": 8906, "name": "盆栽"}, {"id": 2523, "name": "服饰"}, {"id": 10763, "name": "CLOT"}, {"id": 10762, "name": "Kappa"}, {"id": 10832, "name": "The Keter Group"}, {"id": 335, "name": "Uniqlo"}, {"id": 7612, "name": "Disney"}], "category": 17, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 46, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071754248qwOFRB7gbKyi9Il.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t下周一是儿童节，不过工作的各位恐怕没有这么一个假，所以不如趁周末提前给自己一个放松的机会。今天我们提前祝大家 “六一” 儿童节快乐，同时挑选了 6 个充满童趣的设计，你可以买给小朋友，也可以甩甩头说句 “Sorry, I Spent it on Myself”，当然也可以就看看不说话啦。\r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tMini Socks by Etiquette x Miffy\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t今年是 Miffy 这只可爱的小兔子 60 岁生日，Etiquette 与它携手推出了一个联名系列，包含各种色彩缤纷的小袜子，颜色上有米色，蓝色，橙色，黄色等，营造出轻松活泼的氛围，尺寸适合 1 岁到 6 岁的小朋友。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175404H9eNw3ptDxJfXSQA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175404i5hDbYVxMTq4sRmN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175405IlpS6bGifot50ATV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071754056l3RPehwBkfqxQZH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63981481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175406GOPd52LVmr3TDMfJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tLiaison Table by Daniele Ragazzo\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t米兰设计师 Daniele Ragazzo 设计了一款叫做 “Liaison” 的桌子，桌面是一块普通的玻璃，而桌腿则是不锈钢细管搭配彩色小球，看起来就像一个个彩色的棒棒糖。其灵感来源自设计师常常使用的大头针，营造出轻松活泼的装饰效果。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071754068fwRZS2btDJ9ypFU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175407BmjhuOycHr47Y9k6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175407UaXStEIlo01qb9Th.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.38247863\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060717540842w9LeMyZpRjPFWn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.99786325\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175408wtX7zmgVSLQvBEh8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t400% Bearbrick by 《Ted 2》x Medicom\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t即将上映的《Ted 2》和 Medicom Toy 联手推出了一款 400% Bearbrick 玩偶，这只小熊身高 280mm，全身棕色，而且特别可爱地搭配了一条 Ted 小熊特色的小尾巴。目前售价 65 美元，已经开始接受预定，不过将会在 8 月才开始运送。此外 Medicom Toy 还和《Transformers》等推出了联名玩偶，<a href=\"http://www.medicomtoy.co.jp/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看更多详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175408yRg70tbIM4Hzu9N5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175409aKuZYct6Wy5UO1fi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175410FHvLmlpg79w1J0ZR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.79444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175410ftHxX31Lvr9qdVT2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tMickey Plays by Uniqlo x Disney \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t最近，Uniqlo 和 Disney 携手推出了一个叫做 “Mickey Plays” 的联名系列，包括 8 款男装和 4 款童装，作品以网球运动员 Novak Djokovic，Kei Nishikori，Shingo Kunieda 和职业高尔夫选手 Adam Scott 的场上姿态作为灵感来源，加上 Mickey 可爱的模样，整个作品看上去活泼又不失时尚度呢。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175410ZNdhcE4f3eaMK5Dp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175411UxTQyzrFIWX5b2N1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175411PmVNABMOiEabqL3R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175412koJmWur5wEhPZYT7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175412JAlPMH5a78WIkUfz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071754130DJOkIdbRGHXxlui.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175413mMAaj2ibY8BfhnRu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175414EjsbKpL5YqAZOaRi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t3D Knit by The Keter Group\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t塑料公司 The Keter Group 最近推出了一项新技术，可以生产出柔软的 3D 编织外形。这些看起来柔软的编织外表实际上是注射成型的塑料作品，目前公司推出的这一系列作品是各种颜色的盆栽，花盆外面像是穿了一层小毛衣，是不是很像小时候常见的妈妈的手工？\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175415an9cKsyuNWvATIGR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175415aSwjlfmCEvPAbQU5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.14914425\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175415oQ9zLwBrxtsYWhOm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87530562\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175416CuqNxXHDiW8Rvzjm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175417oB1GRqNPnZcU6Aky.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175417iu3fchpQgDbT5HRq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.95843521\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175418MekRjWprbSJhVAu3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.22249389\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175418Z3thaHSGfy4cmlJz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.98410758\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071754197AWNIXzCJ1wQmshR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175419zpWjBIsETlmCU8be.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t2015 Spring/Summer Collection by CLOT x Kappa\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t香港街头品牌 CLOT 和意大利运动品牌 Kappa 携手推出了一个联名系列，其设计灵感来自 KAΨ 大学“兄弟会”与外太空，他们把 CLOT 的 “C” 和 Kappa 的 “K” 融合在一起，设计出全新 Logo，以及各种学院元素，色彩上以红色和蓝色为主打，营造出浓浓的夏日学院感。<a href=\"http://store.clot.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175420QFOf8rhYo7tEuelT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175420pYCexH2IGOa8Eq0d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175421ujQToeSI0b2MtxB6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175421RGoTpXY4BfwJc7Un.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606071754225v7LuyiR93fZoNJs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66794872\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175422hdxKC3LPsTlG5Dq4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607175423ZuLjov52y9tYwRax.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}